<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="21Nov1938"><font color="red">21 November 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your letter of 19 November which came with &hellip; pages 219 to 336 of the paged text. I noted what you say about the wrongly arranged side notes that occur on pages 260 to 308, and I will arrange with our printer for finally revised proofs of those pages &hellip; I will let the printer know also about the correction that you have sent me about Section III of Part II. </div>
